WEBVTT

00:15.440 --> 00:19.410
<i>Spike is great
Making a jewel cake</i>

00:22.500 --> 00:24.150
Me, that's who.

00:24.300 --> 00:26.500
<i>Been saving up my gems
So fine</i>

00:26.650 --> 00:28.700
<i>For a cake
That is divine</i>

00:30.200 --> 00:32.300
Who are you "hooing" at?

00:33.840 --> 00:35.930
I know. They're delicious.

00:38.760 --> 00:42.010
Now you see them,
now you don't.

00:45.260 --> 00:47.530
<i>This is how you make
A jewel cake</i>

00:47.680 --> 00:49.890
<i>Stir in some gems
And then you bake</i>

00:51.780 --> 00:55.010
<i>Gonna eat, eat, eat it up
Gonna--</i>

00:55.770 --> 00:57.690
What happened
to all my jewels?!

01:02.200 --> 01:04.550
I had a bowl full of them here
and now I don't!

01:04.700 --> 01:07.270
Which means,
somebody took them!

01:09.760 --> 01:12.100
Who? That's what I'm asking.
Who?

01:12.250 --> 01:14.070
Who took my jewels?!

01:15.950 --> 01:18.580
Oh, I'm who.

01:18.730 --> 01:21.030
This cake was gonna be
so good.

01:21.180 --> 01:22.220
Why?

01:22.870 --> 01:24.250
Why?

01:30.960 --> 01:33.624
Whyyyyyyyyy??!

01:37.140 --> 01:42.140
Season 3 | Episode 11
Just for Sidekicks

